               <p>(It appeared in evidence that the pot was seen upon the person of the prisoner, by the son of the prosecutor, who pursued her, and she was taken with the pot, which the constable produced; it was deposed to by the prosecutor, who, upon his cross-examination, said, that the prisoner had near relatives of very great respectability.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner left her defence to her Counsel.</p>
